# MMS Web Frontend

Astro + React 18 + Blueprint JS 6.x frontend for the Mileage Management System.

## Quick Start

```bash
# Ensure API is running first (port 3001)
cd ../packages/api && bun run dev

# Start frontend (port 3000)
pnpm dev
```

## Structure

```
src/
├── pages/              # Astro pages
│   ├── index.astro     # Dashboard
│   ├── fleet.astro     # Fleet list
│   ├── schedule.astro  # Schedule table
│   ├── calendar.astro  # Calendar view
│   └── what-if.astro   # What-If Simulator
├── components/         # React components
│   ├── Dashboard.tsx
│   ├── FleetTable.tsx
│   ├── ScheduleTable.tsx
│   ├── CalendarView.tsx
│   ├── WhatIfSimulator.tsx
│   └── Sidebar.tsx
├── layouts/
│   └── MainLayout.astro
├── lib/
│   ├── api.ts          # API client
│   ├── demo-data.ts    # Fallback data generator
│   └── export-utils.ts # Excel/CSV export
└── styles/
    └── global.css
```

## Commands

| Command        | Action                          |
| -------------- | ------------------------------- |
| `pnpm dev`     | Start dev server (port 3000)    |
| `pnpm build`   | Build for production            |
| `pnpm preview` | Preview production build        |

## Tech Stack

- **Astro 5.x** - Static site generator with islands
- **React 18** - UI components
- **Blueprint JS 6.x** - Enterprise UI library
- **TypeScript** - Type safety
